ate at least one dollar per month, or do an hour of </div><div class="t m0 x9 he y85 fff fs3 fc0 sc0 ls6 ws71">voluntary charitable work. This way, as long as there is a </div><div class="t m0 x9 he y86 fff fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws1">kind heart, anyone can participate in a charitable event. </div><div class="t m0 x44 he y88 ffe fs3 fc0 sc0 ls2d ws76">Charity’s Present Situation and Its Historical </div><div class="t m0 x45 he y89 ffe fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Causes </div><div class="t m0 x0 h10 y8a fff fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x42 he y90 fff fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws77">Social polarization is now ve<span class="ls28 ws78">ry serious. Wealthy people </span></div><div class="t m0 x9 he y91 fff fs3 fc0 sc0 ls2e ws79">spend money like water and are extravagant. In contrast, </div><div class="t m0 x9 he y92 fff fs3 fc0 sc0 ls14 ws7a">poor people do not have enough clothes to wear, do not </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
